    out("  FALSIFIED BY: kernel not positive-definite below spectrum")
    out("  UPGRADE TO A: verify resolvent equation for ITCM kernel")
    out("")
    out("Assumption C (Hankel regularity):")
    out("  FALSIFIED BY: essential singularity in kernel, or divergent integral")
    out("  UPGRADE TO A: verify Watson's lemma conditions for ₂F₁ parameters")
    out("  ASSESSMENT: most likely to be closable (technical, not conceptual)")
    out("")
    out("Assumption D (inverse extraction):")
